---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="About | Wild Balance"
	description="The story behind Wild Balance, a handmade merino outdoor clothing brand from Christchurch, New Zealand."
>
	<section class="border-b border-[#d8d1c2]/10 bg-[#11100c] px-5 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-20 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
			<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[#8f9a76]">About</p>
			<h1 class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-normal text-[#f5efe2] sm:text-6xl">
				Handmade merino from Christchurch, built on years at the sewing table.
			</h1>
		</div>
	</section>

	<Section
		title="The next chapter after Morphic Ltd."
		intro="Wild Balance is led by makers with over 12 years of full-time clothing experience. Before this, they ran Morphic Ltd, producing custom merino and cotton clothing from Christchurch and exporting around the world."
	>
		<div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] lg:items-start">
			<div class="material-panel min-h-[24rem]" aria-hidden="true"></div>
			<div class="space-y-6 text-base leading-8 text-[#b8ae9c]">
				<p>
					That background gives Wild Balance a practical foundation: pattern knowledge, fabric
					handling, production discipline, and a clear understanding of what makes a garment
					worth returning to season after season.
				</p>
				<p>
					The brand now turns that experience toward merino outdoor clothing for Southern Alps
					terrain, where comfort, quiet durability, and movement matter more than decoration.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</Section>
</BaseLayout>
